{"tid":1311883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Now新聞台】有上水商店指水貨客影響較遊行更大","createTime":"2019-07-13T11:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T12:13:15.000Z","uid":37554,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"426c8e53b22c84defcdf0c7089ac1630991c33cf","tid":1311883,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:19:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=355284\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355284&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWegAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=bcd8dd3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355284&h=13830a15\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=355284</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】至於較早前的光復上水遊行，有居民指水貨客嚴重影響生活，有商店老闆指水貨客推高租金，影響區內民生，要求當局嚴正執法，主辦單位指有三萬人參加。<br />\n<br />\n遊行隊伍按原定時間約下午三時半從北區運動場出發，遊行以「光復上水」為主題，希望政府執法，減輕水貨客對上水居民的滋擾。<br />\n<br />\n除了水貨客，亦有人希望政府繼續回應撤回修例等的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n有連鎖店拉閘，有職員和顧客在內等候；有商店老闆自費向遊行人士派水，他認為水貨客較遊行的影響更大。<br />\n<br />\n有內地旅客因為遊行影響行程，她表示不理解遊行人士的行動。<br />\n<br />\n遊行期間，有蒙面的男子在商店的閉路電視貼上貼紙遮蓋。有遊行人士在街柱和路牌上以便利貼表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n隊頭約一個多小時抵達終點上水花園，遊行人士之後陸續散去。遊行發起人梁金成認為，即使藥房關門，也不影響遊行的成效。"},{"pid":"c7e0a4bab950558d144b325cb7e4a0d6c5e401c3","tid":1311883,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:20:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91d46c27e02c4a43a97b36c2725b1de4672aacf","tid":1311883,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:22:28.000Z","msg":"原來唔係cctvb 唔怪得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d91370098f021a4b486c21994e1db13a3b29a9e","tid":1311883,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:27:32.000Z","msg":"幫推呀<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M64mk9Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM64mk9Q.png&h=c78aa58c&s={SIZE}\" /> 上面有地址有電話 有電郵 老闆南亞人 但安全起見去的話都要帶口罩。 廣東道340號地下。"},{"pid":"0107a4b944577ffc6eb5924ca6bba475f07e3f09","tid":1311883,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:13:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B1MLPJWtD_o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DB1MLPJWtD_o&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWegAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=4cf85a99\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B1MLPJWtD_o</a>"}]}